  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/f24f57117538b428b28694df42e9a455.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/f24f57117538b428b28694df42e9a455.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TWO OF YOU DO NOT BELONG</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blend into the crowd, act natural, and hunt down the other player in <i>Neon Knives</i>, an award-winning same-screen couch multiplayer game where you’re both the hunter and the hunted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/b5441a0fd857d7ac8b0657d5dfaa405a.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/b5441a0fd857d7ac8b0657d5dfaa405a.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/b5441a0fd857d7ac8b0657d5dfaa405a.mp4?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BATTLEGROUNDS BUILT FOR STEALTH AND TRICKERY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every level offers unique ways to outwit your rival. Sneak unseen between trees, turn tumbleweeds into a distraction, or vanish behind a massive snail just going about its day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/c78a92104edb7e139e49c50c05433b80.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/c78a92104edb7e139e49c50c05433b80.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/c78a92104edb7e139e49c50c05433b80.mp4?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR PLAY STYLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneak through the crowd, bait your mark, attack anything that moves, or take a peek at your buddy’s controls. Each style has its own way to leave chaos and suspicion in your wake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/5bc5bd6892828949cfbf24fda584b108.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/5bc5bd6892828949cfbf24fda584b108.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/5bc5bd6892828949cfbf24fda584b108.mp4?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TWO PLAYERS, ONE CONTROLLER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up to take each other out, as you and your buddy share a single controller or keyboard. Also supports two separate controllers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/ed68020b3ec2b5c2609f56f2aef14a32.avif?t=1771871683\" alt=\"\"data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras_big/ed68020b3ec2b5c2609f56f2aef14a32.webp?t=1771871683 width=1560 height=755 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/f24f57117538b428b28694df42e9a455.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/f24f57117538b428b28694df42e9a455.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TWO OF YOU DO NOT BELONG</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blend into the crowd, act natural, and hunt down the other player in <i>Neon Knives</i>, an award-winning same-screen couch multiplayer game where you’re both the hunter and the hunted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/b5441a0fd857d7ac8b0657d5dfaa405a.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/b5441a0fd857d7ac8b0657d5dfaa405a.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/b5441a0fd857d7ac8b0657d5dfaa405a.mp4?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BATTLEGROUNDS BUILT FOR STEALTH AND TRICKERY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every level offers unique ways to outwit your rival. Sneak unseen between trees, turn tumbleweeds into a distraction, or vanish behind a massive snail just going about its day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/c78a92104edb7e139e49c50c05433b80.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/c78a92104edb7e139e49c50c05433b80.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/c78a92104edb7e139e49c50c05433b80.mp4?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR PLAY STYLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneak through the crowd, bait your mark, attack anything that moves, or take a peek at your buddy’s controls. Each style has its own way to leave chaos and suspicion in your wake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/5bc5bd6892828949cfbf24fda584b108.poster.avif?t=1771871683\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/5bc5bd6892828949cfbf24fda584b108.webm?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/5bc5bd6892828949cfbf24fda584b108.mp4?t=1771871683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TWO PLAYERS, ONE CONTROLLER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up to take each other out, as you and your buddy share a single controller or keyboard. Also supports two separate controllers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras/ed68020b3ec2b5c2609f56f2aef14a32.avif?t=1771871683\" alt=\"\"data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317170/extras_big/ed68020b3ec2b5c2609f56f2aef14a32.webp?t=1771871683 width=1560 height=755 /></span></p>",
